#: ../../talk/index.rst:3
msgid "Talk"
msgstr "Talk"

#: ../../talk/index.rst:5
msgid ""
"Nextcloud Talk offers audio/video and text chat integrated in Nextcloud. It "
"is available as a web interface, desktop client, and mobile apps for Android"
" and iOS."
msgstr ""
"O Nextcloud Talk oferece bate-papo de áudio/vídeo e de texto integrado ao "
"Nextcloud. Está disponível como interface web, cliente para desktop e "
"aplicativos móveis para Android e iOS."

#: ../../talk/index.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can find out more about Nextcloud Talk `on our website "
"<https://nextcloud.com/talk/>`_. Download the desktop and mobile clients "
"from `nextcloud.com/install <https://nextcloud.com/install/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Você pode saber mais sobre o Nextcloud Talk `em nosso site "
"<https://nextcloud.com/talk/>`_. Baixe os clientes para desktop e "
"dispositivos móveis em `nextcloud.com/install "
"<https://nextcloud.com/install/>`_."
